label: dob
comment: Date of birth (DOB) of the individual corresponding to this observation.

label: birthPlace
comment: Place of birth of the individual corresponding to this observation.

label: gender
comment: Gender of the individual corresponding to this observation

label: name
comment: Name of the individual corresponding to this observation

label: phone
comment: Phone number  corresponding to this observation

label: email
comment: Email address of the individual corresponding to this observation

comment: Residential address corresponding to this observation

label: permanentAddress
comment: Permanent address corresponding to this observation

label: businessAddress
comment: Business address corresponding to this observation

label: salutation
comment: Salutation of the individual corresponding to this observation

label: designation
comment: Designation of the individual corresponding to this observation

label: identityInfo
comment: Personal identification information issued by the government.

label: imageURL
comment: The link that points to the picture of the individual or an entity corresponding to this observation.

label: academicQualification
comment: The highest educational qualification of the individual corresponding to this observation.

label: workStatus
comment: The work status indicates whether the individual or entity is actively working, on leave, part-time, full-time, temporary, permanent, retired or in any other specific arrangement.

label: nationality
comment: Represents the nation that the individual corresponding to this observation belongs to.

label: expertise
comment: The advanced knowledge, skills, and understanding acquired through education, training, and experience in diverse agricultural aspects, aiding in productivity, risk reduction, resource conservation, and sustainable profitability.

label: fieldOfResearch
comment: A particular area or subject of study that undergoes investigation, exploration, and systematic examination to acquire fresh knowledge, insights, and comprehension.

label: jurisdiction
comment: The administrative divisions within which the entity holds territorial scope of authority.

label: language
comment: Represents the language(s) that can be used for communicating with an entity or those offered by a service corresponding to this observation.
